oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue on orange) showing the Skyway Drive-In film schedule for May 7-13. Presentations include "Look in Any Window"starring Paul Anka and Ruth Roman, "Giant" starring Rock Hudson and Elizabeth Taylor, and double feature films "Bridges of Dracula"and "Leech Women."
